    "3": {
      "title": "暗环直径测量",
      "correctionMode": "data",
      "dataSource": "device",
      "deviceType": "reading_microscope",
      "dataFields": [
        {
          "key": "ring_m",
          "label": "暗环序号 m",
          "type": "number",
          "required": true,
          "placeholder": "如 10"
        },
        {
          "key": "reading_left_mm",
          "label": "左读数",
          "type": "number",
          "unit": "mm",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 30,
          "required": true
        },
        {
          "key": "reading_right_mm",
          "label": "右读数",
          "type": "number",
          "unit": "mm",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 30,
          "required": true
        },
        {
          "key": "diameter_D_mm",
          "label": "直径 Dₘ",
          "type": "number",
          "unit": "mm",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 20,
          "required": false,
          "placeholder": "可由左右读数差求得"
        }
      ],
      "assistMock": {
        "errorType": "暗环读数",
        "detail": "左右读数差与直径不一致，或环序号记录混乱。",
        "feedback": "**原因分析**：读数误差与回程间隙会直接影响 Dₘ² 计算。\n\n**纠错指导**：\n1. **编号1**：复核 D = |右读数 − 左读数|。\n2. **编号2**：检查环序号是否与数据表一一对应。",
        "marks": [
          {
            "x": 276,
            "y": 194,
            "w": 122,
            "h": 106,
            "n": 1
          },
          {
            "x": 532,
            "y": 264,
            "w": 108,
            "h": 90,
            "n": 2
          }
        ]
      },
      "guidePath": "steps/3.md"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "曲率半径或波长计算",
      "correctionMode": "data",
      "dataSource": "device",
      "deviceType": "newton_analyzer",
      "dataFields": [
        {
          "key": "delta_m",
          "label": "环序差 Δm",
          "type": "number",
          "required": true,
          "placeholder": "如 5"
        },
        {
          "key": "delta_D2_mm2",
          "label": "Dₘ² − Dₙ²",
          "type": "number",
          "unit": "mm²",
          "min": 0,
          "required": true
        },
        {
          "key": "lambda_nm",
          "label": "波长 λ",
          "type": "number",
          "unit": "nm",
          "min": 400,
          "max": 700,
          "required": false,
          "placeholder": "钠光约 589.3"
        },
        {
          "key": "radius_R_mm",
          "label": "曲率半径 R",
          "type": "number",
          "unit": "mm",
          "min": 100,
          "max": 10000,
          "required": false
        },
        {
          "key": "error_pct",
          "label": "相对误差",
          "type": "number",
          "unit": "%",
          "required": false
        }
      ],
      "assistMock": {
        "errorType": "结果计算",
        "detail": "公式代换单位不统一，或 λ、R 数量级明显偏离合理范围。",
        "feedback": "**原因分析**：单位换算错误是光学实验最常见计算失误。\n\n**纠错指导**：\n1. **编号1**：将 D 换算为 m 后再代入公式。\n2. **编号2**：钠光 λ 约为 589 nm，R 通常在米级，请核对结果量级。",
        "marks": [
